query:
SELECT t.id as tenant_id, t.name as company_name, u.email, u.name as user_name, ts.id as subscription_id, ts.status as subscription_status
FROM tenants t
LEFT JOIN users u ON u.tenantId = t.id
LEFT JOIN tenantSubscriptions ts ON ts.tenantId = t.id
ORDER BY t.id DESC
LIMIT 20;
